    <table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0" width="100%">
    <tr>
        <td id="descriptionArea">
            <p>On the NASS ePayment <b>order description page</b>, the <b>"Pay Now" button is visible but does not respond when tapped</b>.</p>

<p>Even after clicking the button, no action is triggered—user is not navigated to the next step (PIN/payment processing), and no loader or error message is shown. This prevents users from completing the payment flow.</p>

<h2><a name="StepstoReproduce%3A"></a>Steps to Reproduce:</h2>

<ol>
	<li>Open FastPay Personal app</li>
	<li>Navigate to <b>NASS ePayment</b></li>
	<li>Enter valid bill / customer details</li>
	<li>Proceed to the <b>order description page</b></li>
	<li>Tap on the <b>"Pay Now" button</b></li>
</ol>


<h2><a name="ActualResult%3A"></a>Actual Result:</h2>

<ul>
	<li>"Pay Now" button does not respond</li>
	<li>No navigation / no loader / no feedback</li>
	<li>User remains stuck on the same page</li>
</ul>


<h2><a name="ExpectedResult%3A"></a>Expected Result:</h2>

<ul>
	<li>On tapping "Pay Now", system should:
	<ul>
		<li>Trigger next step (PIN entry / processing)</li>
		<li>Show loader or feedback</li>
		<li>Proceed with payment flow</li>
	</ul>
	</li>
</ul>


<h2><a name="Severity%3A"></a>Severity:</h2>

<p><b>High</b></p>
            <br/>
        </td>
